<paragraph id="D1DCBDA71B3218DEEFA944F7DA070F9E" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
<taxonomicName id="675FD6CB6D6572742767946ADE1C23EE" authority="L." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Adonis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="103" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aestivalis">
Adonis 
<normalizedToken id="7BD271C39A5CFE3C9FA1A701AE4A699D" originalValue="aestivális" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">aestivalis</normalizedToken>
<authorityName id="C818EAB331244B699F956D2ADA51F05F" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">L.</authorityName>
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="9561F84E10F85AE8EF15FF87197B2E5E" pageId="null" pageNumber="103" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="21874BE5D4D0EF9611DB279AF66B293D" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Sommer-Adonis</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="9ED4FB799C661BFA4DE79F8ADB366F4F" pageId="null" pageNumber="103" type="description">
<paragraph id="7A2EB77F70A50D05AC6142B9615425A1" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="45CDA03186C0CD7CCBDC1F37E25DAFA6" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Adonis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="103" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="flammea">
<emphasis id="81E168861268C207A9EF964547897D96" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">A. flammea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="7FDD574A2CDEEA12817E8078FF6D5ECD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
Stengel kahl; 
<normalizedToken id="C83FA0DB93D585F77A3D9837D2764DCB" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="BE148688A86A9F202D27439908170B94" originalValue="Früchtchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Fruechtchen</normalizedToken>
dicht stehend
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B692A29C239C130BF10734E0EFA0088D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
<normalizedToken id="5E7CCA8E6B0B2E7A794E3F1C6940092B" originalValue="Blütenboden" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Bluetenboden</normalizedToken>
nicht sichtbar
</emphasis>
)
<emphasis id="1231FAE34DF59A2090C92AAB7CA8ACF8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
; oft 2 
<normalizedToken id="C096D2B337A25698A0FD4BAB64477ED7" originalValue="Zähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Zaehne</normalizedToken>
am Bauch
</emphasis>
(obere Seite), Ansatzstelle fast so breit wie die 
<normalizedToken id="0C4A3EEC91CAC98D46341A85B51F7D79" originalValue="größte" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">groesste</normalizedToken>
Breite der Frucht; 
<emphasis id="A1BD17B6269D6A456783153274A41B76" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Schnabel nicht schwarz</emphasis>
, die Spitze der Frucht bildend. - 
<normalizedToken id="24299C9CCF736FFF2958BDE3FF2C8E8A" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="A687EE5AA25A00DF9854A21B9ADBE5C0" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="60F0DF721E00C44F197EF3767410C6BC" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="3616B6EA88A66810841D61AA89C6E24C" originalValue="Frühsommer" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Fruehsommer</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A7BCCAD5D4269B6548B99376C16E28FB" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
<emphasis id="0C5A2A92DE4440133015D287F32A8859" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="334DEAC9D1B0151C0C2C3C9E4077821D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">32:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="285007AFC195EB772C75126370AC3E64" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Langlet 1927, Gregory 1941, Kurita 1963).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="72133C0A568C892686008AC25FDFD2B1" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
<emphasis id="FB2A9DF8894ABB6A472DE7C2C60F5771" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="CFB64C87F46DBCFCFE116812BDAA0E16" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Adonis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="103" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="flammea">
<emphasis id="FD73FB893C3001868FCA16EF79CC4A29" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">A. flammea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2F16B54467FCABC9FE5069F78DCE07D0" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
<emphasis id="0F25BBDCCF0C7023618F131000FF1AB0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="19B50EA066A4696387D46A992AA8A828" originalValue="Südeuropäisch-asiatische" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Suedeuropaeisch-asiatische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="47B0B99AD58F722C68C85C5AFBA53047" originalValue="Nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 54° NB (kommt in England nicht vor); 
<normalizedToken id="E99BBFFDADE7E93EF5A5D00DEC43C10A" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Nordafrika, Kleinasien, Mesopotamien, westlicher Himalaja; 
<normalizedToken id="1AF7245C93586378D8451C703E2A0FAC" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Zentralasien (Tienschan, Mongolei). Verbreitungskarte von Meusel (1965). - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="72B14BCBE157B26862393223A3771C2B" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Doubs, 
<normalizedToken id="F845BB469A13D2AB4417D1E3A559B341" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Jura, Gegend von Belfort, Sundgau, Vogesen, 
<normalizedToken id="F088F900040FC98CA4A04FD355D89B71" originalValue="Elsaß" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Elsass</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="C8302D8A61A23592D6751BD7F18F79F6" originalValue="Süddeutschland" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Sueddeutschland</normalizedToken>
, Nordschweiz, Zentral- und 
<normalizedToken id="3D9CFAE29AD559F13A6E8556177D84A1" originalValue="Südalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">Suedalpen</normalizedToken>
. Als Ackerunkraut selten geworden, aber noch 
<normalizedToken id="EE71E1D48762B90DD3DFF6C7264BE5FC" originalValue="häufiger" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">haeufiger</normalizedToken>
als 
<emphasis id="9905784DC3C0E685B34F33E41F95514C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="103">
<taxonomicName id="B4B4A58DA1801577A36EFB772B17A431" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Adonis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="103" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="flammea">A. flammea</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
